{{Infobox rockunit | name = Anguilla Formation | image = | caption = | type = [[Formation (stratigraphy)|Formation]] | age = [[Neogene]] | period = Neogene | prilithology = | otherlithology = | namedfor = | namedby = | region = | country = [[Anguilla]] | coordinates = | unitof = | subunits = | underlies = | overlies = | thickness = | extent = | area = | map = | map_caption = }}
The '''Anguilla Formation''' is a [[Formation (geology)|geologic formation]] in [[Anguilla]]. It preserves [[fossils]] dating back to the [[Neogene]] [[Period (geology)|period]].
