Mesoregions may be defined on the basis of morpholithogenic conditions and spatial connection.<ref>Recent Landform Evolution: The Carpatho-Balkan-Dinaric Region, edited by Dénes Lóczy, Miloš Stankoviansky, Adam Kotarba [https://books.google.com/books?id=GClF-4rtvoIC&pg=PA325 p. 325]</ref>

